<section class="section section--ice" aria-labelledby="apart-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="apart__layout">
      <div class="apart__text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our approach</p>
        <h2 id="apart-heading">One platform.<br />Total mastery.</h2>
        <div class="accent-bar"></div>
        <p class="apart__lead">
          Most marketing agencies treat LinkedIn as one checkbox on a long list of channels.
          We treat it as the only one. That focus is not a limitation — it is a deliberate choice
          that makes everything we do sharper and more accountable than what a generalist agency
          can offer.
        </p>
        <p class="apart__body">
          We know how the LinkedIn algorithm rewards consistency. We know which ad formats perform
          at each stage of the B2B funnel. We know what makes a B2B buyer stop scrolling, read,
          and act. We know because LinkedIn is all we do, every day, for clients across industries
          and markets worldwide.
        </p>
        <p class="apart__body">
          Strategy, platform audit, and performance reporting come with every engagement — not
          sold as extras.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="apart__pillars" aria-label="Core advantages">
        <div class="apart__pillar">
          <span class="apart__pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">◎</span>
          <h3 class="apart__pillar-title">LinkedIn-only depth</h3>
          <p>We go deeper on this platform than any generalist agency can. Every recommendation is grounded in current mechanics, product updates, and B2B audience behaviour on LinkedIn specifically.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="apart__pillar">
          <span class="apart__pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">◎</span>
          <h3 class="apart__pillar-title">Global client base</h3>
          <p>We work with B2B companies from established multinationals to high-growth challengers, across industries and markets worldwide.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="apart__pillar">
          <span class="apart__pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">◎</span>
          <h3 class="apart__pillar-title">Everything included</h3>
          <p>Strategy, platform audit, and performance reporting are part of every engagement. Not upsells. Not extras.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .apart__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .apart__lead {
    font-size: var(--font-size-md);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .apart__body {
    color: var(--color-slate);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .apart__pillars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
  }

  .apart__pillar {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: var(--border-thin);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-cyan);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
  }

  .apart__pillar-icon {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-cyan);
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .apart__pillar-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-deep-navy);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .apart__pillar p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-slate);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .apart__layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .apart__pillars {
      padding-top: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
